reviewText: This Video it is audio visual tool to improve our knowledge of Kata Jion , Sochin and Unsu doing for the best master in a World. If you are a Shotokan instructor include step by step Katas details and bunkai doing by Tanaka Sensei (Jion), Yahora sensei Unsu and Ozaka Sensei Sochin. It is like a train with then and learn theirs Kata secrets.
